  <div class="journal-entry-float-day"><span class="name">Saturday</span></div><div class="journal-entry-float-date"><span class="month">Dec</span><span class="date">17</span><span class="year">2011</span></div>
  
  
  
  <div class="journal-entry-text">
  
      
      <h2 class="title">
    
        
    
        <a class="journal-entry-navigation-current" href="/blog/2011/12/17/im-the-16th-most-viral-person-on-the-internet-according-to-g.html">I'm the 16th most viral person on the Internet, according to&nbsp;Gizmodo</a>  
     
         
    
      </h2>
      
       <div class="journal-entry-tag journal-entry-tag-post-title"><span class="posted-on">   <img title="Date" alt="Date" class="inline-icon date-icon" rel="dark" src="/universal/images/transparent.png" />Saturday, December 17, 2011 at 18:22</span> |  <span class="posted-by">  <a href="/blog/author/baratunde"> <img title="Author" alt="Author" class="inline-icon user-registered-icon" rel="dark" src="/universal/images/transparent.png" />baratunde</a></span> |  <span class="tagged-with">tagged <span class="tag-element"><a rel="tag" href="/blog/tag/internet"> <img title="Tag" alt="Tag" class="inline-icon tag-icon" rel="dark" src="/universal/images/transparent.png" />Internet</a></span>, <span class="tag-element"><a rel="tag" href="/blog/tag/media-appearances"> <img title="Tag" alt="Tag" class="inline-icon tag-icon" rel="dark" src="/universal/images/transparent.png" />Media Appearances</a></span></span>  </div> 

    
  
      
      <div class="body">
  
        
        
        
          <p><a title="Viral Infection by naturalhomecures34, on Flickr" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/51438986@N07/5018792385/"><img src="http://farm5.staticflickr.com/4149/5018792385_84d6b8a575_z.jpg" alt="Viral Infection" width="640" height="480" /></a></p>
<div></div>
<div>Sounds pretty nasty right? See, it's <a href="http://gizmodo.com/5863333/meet-the-25-most-viral-people-on-the-internet">right there</a>&nbsp;on the Internet. Must be true.</div>

        
  
          
  
         
  
